These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, october, september, august, november, february, march
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: metal, r&b, funk, gospel, classical, rock, dubstep
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
 3. the fan classical is on the right of the fan dubstep##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is between the fan funk and the fan classical##2
 5. the fan r&b is on the right of the fan rock##1
 6. the fan r&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the fan metal is between the fan gospel and the fan funk##2
 8. the fan r&b is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the fan funk##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Birthday   | august | july | march | october    | september | november   | february    |
| Music-Genre         | rock  | r&b   | gospel | metal | funk   | dubstep | classical |

