.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, lemonade, almond-milk, sprite, juice, hot-chocolate
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, december, june, march, october, january, july
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Beverage          | sprite | lemonade | juice | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | 7up      | almond-milk  |
| Birthday   | january | march  | july     | june     | october  | may | december |

