 3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person drinking juice##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
