.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: plum, orangemelon, cabbage, corn, potato, artichoke, orange
The people have 7 different jobs:  designer, writer, architect, manager, coach, engineer, chef
 1. the person eating orange is on the left of the architect##1
 2. the person eating potato is on the right of the coach##1
 3. the engineer is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the coach##1
 5. the designer is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 6. the manager is between the person eating cabbage and the engineer##2
 7. the person eating plum is in the middle##1
 8. the manager is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 9. the person eating orangemelon is the writer##1
10. the designer is the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Food      | cabbage    | potato  | corn  | plum  | orange      | artichoke       | orangemelon |
| Job   | coach | manager | engineer | chef | designer | architect | writer  |

