1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in october##2
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's birthday is in may##1
9. the person who's birthday is in april is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Birthday   | may      | april | october | december | january      | february      | november |
| City     | hamburg | colone | liverpool       | new-york | hannover | marseilles | london |

