4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who growsdaffodil##2
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who growsrose is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
