 6. the dancer is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is the dancer##1
 8. the coach is the person who growstulip##1
 9. the person who growsiris is between the person who growstulip and the police-officer##2
10. the chef is on the left of the coach##1

