.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, trike, quad-bike, motorbike, train, tram
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, argentine, indonesian, british, pakistani, colombian, nigerian
 1. the pakistani is on the left of the british##1
 2. the japanese is on the left of the indonesian##1
 3. the colombian is on the far left##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the pakistani is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person driving the train is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the tram##2
 7. the argentine is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the japanese is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the airplane##2
11. the pakistani is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Transport   | trike  | motorbike   | airplane         | scooter     | tram              | train    | quad-bike     |
| Nationality        | colombian | argentine | pakistani | british | nigerian | japanese | indonesian |

